on or off for this interrogation?

28:55.400 --> 28:56.818
-What?
-The cameras...

28:57.193 --> 28:59.612
You want me to put them off
to enjoy a little creative freedom

28:59.696 --> 29:01.948
with the frat boy here
until he's ready to break?

29:08.163 --> 29:10.582
Ah. There's my little Epsilon.

29:10.665 --> 29:13.251
Hey, just because you're a fox
doesn't mean I'm gonna talk to ya.

29:13.334 --> 29:15.128
Cool. You think I'm a fox?

29:15.211 --> 29:16.588
That's so sweet.

29:16.671 --> 29:19.549
Lane, can I paint you a picture
that's just as ugly

29:19.632 --> 29:22.135
as that ridiculous portrait of you
back at the frat house?

29:22.302 --> 29:24.429
I painted that myself and it's dope.

29:24.512 --> 29:27.098
Wow, you should never paint again
and you never will

29:27.182 --> 29:30.018
because I think you're gonna go
to prison for murdering Cassie.

29:30.351 --> 29:33.396
-I didn't kill anyone.
-Yet, you jumped in your car and run.

29:33.480 --> 29:35.148
That doesn't scream innocent to me.

29:35.231 --> 29:37.400
Because I stiffed the party bus guy.

29:37.901 --> 29:39.694
And stole the school mascot, too,

29:39.778 --> 29:41.196
which I still cant find.

29:41.279 --> 29:43.948
And I sent some nasty texts to Cassie.

29:44.407 --> 29:46.618
But it's because she might be
the only chick on campus

29:46.701 --> 29:48.495
who doesn't want
to have some sex with me.

29:49.996 --> 29:50.955
You wanna know what I think?

29:51.039 --> 29:54.667
I think she embarrassed you
on that bus in front of your brothers.

29:54.751 --> 29:57.045
I think you followed her
to the parking garage

29:57.128 --> 29:59.923
and fought with her,
maybe her fall was just an accident?

30:00.006 --> 30:01.090
You tell me.

30:01.883 --> 30:03.426
All right, you and Villa...

30:03.968 --> 30:07.138
Rumor mill out in the pen was on point
you guys click like crazy.

30:08.139 --> 30:09.349
Come on, man. Talk to me.

30:09.432 --> 30:12.352
-Is it more than a work thing?
-It's just a work thing.

30:12.435 --> 30:15.271
