30:19.317 --> 30:21.486
-Everything is fine.
-Everything is not fine.

30:23.071 --> 30:27.075
You know, I'm here
if you wanna hang, chat about it.

30:27.784 --> 30:30.203
-I'm good, yeah.
-Okay. All right.

30:30.620 --> 30:32.872
The bruising on Cassie's arms
from where you grabbed her

30:32.956 --> 30:34.374
tells me you got physical.

30:35.708 --> 30:37.752
Come on.
